cinnamon.engine.utils

Class Sort<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.utils.Sort<E>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Merge

    public abstract class Sort<E>
extends Object

    Base class for comparison-based sorting algorithms. This class provides a swappable the Comparison to establish an ordering between objects as well as an ordering validation method isOrdered(Object[], boolean).
